'''Swing-bop''' was a style of [[Music/Legends|music]] popular circa [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]]. [[Umjing Baab]] and [[Umjing Baab and His Swinging Trio|His Swinging Trio]] were among the [[Rughja]] musicians who played swing-bop. Their style of swing-bop involved each band member playing ten or more instruments at once.

